             was indicted for <rs id="t17890225-64-off292" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17890225-64-off292" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890225-64-off292" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously and feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890225-64-victim585" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t17890225-64-victim585" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
