                     <interp inst="t17890225-64-verdict294" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY, of stealing only
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17890225-64-punish295" type="punishmentDescription">
